data.description: SHOWINGS RESTART THIS FRIDAY, 8/13! - Nice Sunnybrook Townhome Backing Open Space And Super Convenient To Route 422 & Phila. Premium Outlets.  Modern Floor Plan Offering Great Room On Lower Level With Access To Oversize Deck.  Spacious Living Room With Hardwood Floors, Large Kitchen With Center Island & Tile Flooring Plus Bright & Open Sun Rm Overlooking Deck & Open Space.  All Good Size Bedrooms Including The Owner's Suite With Vaulted Ceilings, Walk-In Closet & Nicely Appointed Full Bath With Soaking Tub .  Ample Closet & Storage Space Throughout Plus A 1-Car Garage.  Addition Remarks Available Shortly.  Showings Start Wednesday, July 21st - Schedule Your Visit Today!
